Quest OS Licensing
==================

Quest OS uses per-file SPDX license identifiers.

The license for each source file is the SPDX expression in that file's
`SPDX-License-Identifier` line. If a file does not contain an SPDX identifier,
its license status must be checked before redistribution.

Unless a file states otherwise, Quest OS-authored source is intended to be
licensed under GPL-2.0-family terms. Some files in this repository are imported
or adapted from upstream projects including Linux, U-Boot, libfdt, Linux UAPI,
and nolibc. Those files remain under their upstream licenses.

See `THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md` for the vendored component inventory and license
summary. Preserve all SPDX identifiers, copyright notices, and upstream license
headers when redistributing or modifying this code.
